### ========================================
### TRAVEL BOOKING API - TEST ENDPOINTS
### Backend: http://localhost:8080
### ========================================

### 1. HEALTH CHECK
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tours
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. REGISTER NEW USER
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "testuser@gmail.com",
  "password": "123456",
  "phone": "0123456789"
}

### 3. LOGIN (Get Token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### 4. LOGIN AS ADMIN (Use this token for protected routes)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@gmail.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Save the token from response above, then use it below:
@token = YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

### 5. GET ALL TOURS (Public)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tours
Content-Type: application/json

### 6. GET TOURS WITH FILTERS
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tours?tourType=DOMESTIC&page=0&size=12
Content-Type: application/json

### 7. GET TOUR BY SLUG
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tours/slug/du-lich-ha-long
Content-Type: application/json

### 8. GET CATEGORIES
GET http://localhost:8080/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json

### 9. GET USER PROFILE (Protected - Need Token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 10. GET MY BOOKINGS (Protected - Need Token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/bookings/my-bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 11. ADMIN: GET DASHBOARD STATS (Protected - Need Admin Token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/dashboard/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 12. ADMIN: GET ALL USERS (Protected - Need Admin Token)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/admin/users
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 13. CREATE BOOKING (Protected - Need Token)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/bookings
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "tourId": 1,
  "startDate": "2025-10-15",
  "customerName": "Test User",
  "customerEmail": "testuser@gmail.com",
  "customerPhone": "0123456789",
  "numAdults": 2,
  "numChildren": 1,
  "numInfants": 0,
  "specialRequests": "Vegetarian meals"
}

### 14. GET TOUR SCHEDULES
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tour-schedules?tourId=1
Content-Type: application/json

### 15. WISHLISTS - Add Tour to Wishlist (Protected)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/wishlists/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 16. WISHLISTS - Get My Wishlist (Protected)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/wishlists
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 17. GET TOUR FAQS
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tour-faqs?tourId=1
Content-Type: application/json

### 18. SEARCH TOURS
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tours/search?keyword=ha%20long
Content-Type: application/json

### 19. GET LOCATIONS (for filter)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tours/locations
Content-Type: application/json

### 20. GET SWAGGER API DOCS
GET http://localhost:8080/swagger-ui.html

### ========================================
### NOTES:
### - Replace {{token}} with actual JWT token from login response
### - Admin credentials: admin@gmail.com / admin123
### - Test user: testuser@gmail.com / 123456
### ========================================
